==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Upsend
<hw>Up*send"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To send, cast, or
throw up.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>As when some island situate afar . . . ⟦br⟧
<qex>Upsends</qex> a smoke to heaven.</q>
<rj><qau>Cowper.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Upset</ent>⟦br⟧
